<div id="c9">
<p>In school, the two most influential courses on my ways of thinking were those relating to formal logic, and those relating to methodology in the social sciences.  Just learning about &#8216;conceptualization&#8217; and &#8216;operationalization&#8217; of the concepts in language was enough to shake up half of my worldview.</p>

<p class="posted">posted by Antonio
